data.description: Built in 2022, this home has been meticulously maintained and offers many upgrades and recent updates! Great curb appeal with exterior brick, stone accents and full landscaping! The Starkville floor plan offers 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, wide hallways, split bedroom floorplan, neutral flooring, 36 inch vanities and spacious dining area.  Chef's kitchen awaits with sleek granite counters, marble backsplash, island with breakfast bar seating, gas range, stainless steel appliances and walk in pantry!  Primary suite and bath offers double sinks, oversized walk in shower and walk in closet! Ideal outdoor living space offers 352 feet of extended patio space and a covered pergola! This community also offers park and gated pool!
